(1340, 1, '2012-06-12 23:04:51', '2012-06-12 23:04:51', 'Minimise administration time and cost, let your employees book a flu vaccination <a href="http://www.bookflujab.co.uk/">online</a>. It is quick and easy. All you need is just to ask for a client code before the time of booking and send the code to your staff along with a link to the booking page.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Free online booking ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'free-online-booking', '', '', '2012-09-04 10:47:24', '2012-09-04 10:47:24', '', 0, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/?post_type=features&#038;p=1340', 0, 'features', '', 0),
