(413, 1, '2011-11-25 11:34:28', '2011-11-25 11:34:28', '<span style="color: #000000;">Flu Fighters make vaccinating your staff against seasonal flu a simple procedure. </span><span style="color: #000000;">Just tell us the time, place and number of influenza vaccinations required and we do the rest. </span><span style="color: #000000;">Our experienced team of nurses deliver a fully mobile flu vaccination service wherever you are in the UK with minimum disruption. </span><span style="color: #000000;">Our nurses have all the equipment needed and we will ensure all the influenza vaccinations are delivered to the highest possible clinical standards. </span><span style="color: #000000;">Once you have decided to offer your employees the perk of a flu jab, we help you achieve maximum take-up levels. We help to ensure that your staff understand the health benefits that flu jabs can offer both at work and at home. </span><span style="color: #000000;">The best time to vaccinate your staff is between October and December. </span>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000;">What to expect on the Day?</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">On your chosen day the trained nurse(s) will arrive 15 minutes before the flu vaccination service is due to begin, with all the medical equipment required, and will ensure the vaccinations are delivered to the highest <span style="color: #000000;">clinical standard d</span></span><span style="color: #000000;">isruption to you and your staff is minimal. It only takes a couple of minutes for the nurse to give the flu vaccination - through a small injection in the upper arm.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">All we require from you is:</span>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">A private room</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">Two chairs</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">A table</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">Access to a telephone</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">Drinking water</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">A washbasin</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">If there are windows in the room, blinds or curtains to provide staff privacy</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="/about-us/">Read more about our company</a>.</span></div>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Corporate Flu Vaccination', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'our-service', '', '', '2012-07-25 10:17:08', '2012-07-25 10:17:08', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/?page_id=413', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1025, 2, '2012-01-12 09:18:29', '2012-01-12 09:18:29', '<span style="color: #000000;">We are the UK arm of the European Vaccination Group, which has delivered more than 2.5 million vaccines over the last 10 years, including to the blue-chip companies Shell, Motorola and Siemens.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Flu Fighters is our campaign to promote the benefits of vaccination in the workplace, engage staff and maximise take up. Flu Fighters has also been designed to reflect the commitment of our team to offering the best vaccination service with the highest levels of dedication and clinical excellence.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Our team includes 80 dedicated nurses and we vaccinate all across UK.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">We are here to keep your team fighting fit this winter.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">If you have any questions about our service or would like to find out more, please contact us:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Phone: <strong>0845 521 0030</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Email: <a title="Email us..." accesskey="e" tabindex="23" href="mailto:in%66o@flufight%65r%73.or%67.u%6B"><span style="color: #000000;">info@flufighters.org.uk</span></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Write:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> The Health Station (UK) Limited,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> 21a Brand Street,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> Hitchin, Hertfordshire,</span>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> SG5 1JE</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">To book call <strong>0845 521 0030</strong> and let Flu Fighters help defend your organisation.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="/get-a-quote/">Get a quote</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2012-07-26 14:28:35', '2012-07-26 14:28:35', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.net/?page_id=1025', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(1641, 2, '2012-06-18 10:20:52', '2012-06-18 10:20:52', '<div>\r\n\r\n<strong><img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/dr-bill-holmes.jpg" alt="Dr Bill Holmes" width="120" height="146" align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10" />“</strong>We pride ourselves in delivering our vaccination programmes to the highest clinical standards. Our primary focus is the safety and comfort of those receiving the vaccine.\r\n\r\nThe flu vaccines that we use are the same as those provided by the NHS, manufactured under guidance from the World Health Organisation, and in 2012 will also protect against swine flu.\r\n\r\nOur customers receive the best possible service and highest levels of medical care. Our vaccinations are delivered by qualified nurses who have received training in flu vaccine delivery. Nurses conduct the onsite clinics with comprehensive medical kits.\r\n\r\nWe offer a 24-hour telephone medical support-line in case your employees have any queries regarding their vaccination.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions regarding our clinical processes and practices, please <a title="Email Dr Bill Holmes..." tabindex="24" href="mailto:drbillholmes@evguk.co.uk">contact me</a>.<strong>”</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/dr-bill-holmes-signature.jpg" alt="Dr Bill Holmes'' signature" width="100" height="33" />\r\n\r\nDr Bill Holmes F.R.C.P, F.R.C.G.P, D.Occ.Med\r\nMedical Director\r\n\r\nTo book call <strong>0845 521 0030 </strong>and let Flu Fighters help defend your organisation.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Clinical Excellence', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '325-revision-12', '', '', '2012-06-18 10:20:52', '2012-06-18 10:20:52', '', 325, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/325-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
