(226, 2, '2011-11-21 14:03:44', '2011-11-21 14:03:44', '<strong>About Hepatitis A</strong>\n\nHepatitis A is a viral infection which can cause severe liver disease. The viral infection is usually spread by contaminated food and water.\n\n<strong>Vaccination recommendation</strong>\n\nEffective hepatitis A vaccines are available, and boosters last up to 25 years.\n\nFind out what vaccines you need by selecting your destination <span style="text-decoration: underline;">here</span>.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Hepatitis A', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '211-autosave', '', '', '2011-11-21 14:03:44', '2011-11-21 14:03:44', '', 211, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/211-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
