(197, 1, '2011-10-10 00:50:06', '2011-10-10 00:50:06', '<style>\r\ntd {\r\nvertical-align: top;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td  width="170">\r\n<label for="title">Title (*) </label>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n[select* title  id:title include_blank "Mr" "Mrs" "Miss" "Ms" "Dr"]\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="first-name">First Name (*)</label></td>\r\n<td>[text* first-name id:first-name]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="last-name">Last Name (*)</label></td>\r\n<td>[text* last-name id:last-name]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="job-title">Job Title</label></td>\r\n<td>[text job-title id:job-title]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="organisation">Organisation</label></td>\r\n<td>[text organisation id:organisation]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="phone">Phone no (*)</label></td>\r\n<td>[text* phone id:phone]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="email">E-mail (*)</label></td>\r\n<td>[email* email id:email]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="address">Address and Postcode (*)</label></td>\r\n<td>[textarea* address id:address x3]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="employees">Number of employees (*)</label></td>\r\n<td>[select* employees id:employees "Less than 60" "60-89" "90-119" "120-149" "150-179" "180-299" "More than 300"]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="vaccination_before">Have you offered a flu vaccination before</label></td>\r\n<td>[select* vaccination_before id:vaccination_before "Yes" "No"]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><label for="message">Any other information you would like us to know:</label></td>\r\n<td>[textarea message id:message x3]</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n\r\n[submit "Send"]\nNew quote from Flu Fighters\n[first-name] [last-name] <admin@konscript.com>\nReceived a new quote from flufighters.org.uk!\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nSubmitted on [_date] - [_time]\r\nSubmitted by anonymous user: [[wpcf7.remote_ip]]\r\n\r\nSubmitted values are:\r\n\r\nTitle: [title]\r\nFirst Name: [first-name]\r\nLast Name: [last-name]\r\nJob Title: [job-title]\r\nOrganisation: [organisation]\r\nPhone no: [phone]\r\nE-mail: [email]\r\nAddress and Postcode: \r\n[address]\r\n\r\nNumber of employees: [employees]\r\nHave you offered a flu vaccination before: [vaccination_before]\r\n\r\nAny other information you would like us to know:\r\n[message]\nquote@flufighters.org.uk, andrew@evguk.co.uk\n\n\n\n1\nYour Flu Fighters Quote\ninfo@flufighters.org.uk <info@flufighters.org.uk>\nDear [title] [last-name],\r\n\r\n<strong>Thank you for requesting a quote.</strong>\r\n\r\nOne of our staff will be in touch with you shortly to make sure we are able to give you the best\r\nservice.\r\n\r\nWe will call you to discuss your individual requirements in more detail such as: your anticipated take\r\nup, shift patterns (which may involve more than one visit), the number of locations you would like us\r\nto visit and to find out if you would benefit from using a dedicated booking system. All this will allow\r\nus to propose the most cost efficient way of delivering your service whilst at the same time offering\r\nadvice on how to boost take up. Having done this, we will agree a final quote with you.\r\n\r\nYou don''t need to confirm doses now. We''ll give you a quote, and up to 7 days before delivery, we\r\nwill agree an accurate figure with you of the total number of vaccines you require. In this way, you are\r\nable to adjust the final number, helping to save you money - or benefit from further volume discount.\r\n\r\nWe will shortly be in touch.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://flufighters.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/logo-flufighters1.png" alt="" border="0" />\r\n\r\n<strong>The Flu Fighters</strong>\r\n0845 521 0030\r\n21a Brand Street, Hitchin, Hertfordshire, SG5 1JE\r\nhttp://www.flufighters.org.uk\n[email]\n\n\n1\nThank you, we have received your inquiry. We will contact you soon for your personalised quote. quote@flufighters.org.uk, andrew@evguk.co.uk, lyncousins@evguk.co.uk\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact administrator by other way.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact administrator by other way.\nValidation errors occurred. Please confirm the fields and submit it again.\nPlease accept the terms to proceed.\nEmail address seems invalid.\nThis field is mandatory.\nFailed to upload file.\nThis file type is not allowed.\nThis file is too large.\nFailed to upload file. Error occurred.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nYour answer is not correct.\non_sent_ok: "location.replace(''http://www.flufighters.org.uk/thank-you-for-your-enquiry/'');"', 'dlvs-quote', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dlvs-quote', '', '', '2012-12-22 23:11:13', '2012-12-22 23:11:13', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/wpcf7_contact_form/dlvs-quote/', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
(1884, 1, '2012-07-18 20:06:28', '2012-07-18 20:06:28', 'European Vaccination Group (UK) Limited (EVGUK) does not make the names and addresses of its customers or their employees available to any third party organisations.\n\nEVGUK fully complies with Data Protection legislation and medical confidentiality guidelines.\n\nTo book call 0845 521 0030 and let Flu Fighters help defend your organisation.', 'Privacy Statement', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1883-revision', '', '', '2012-07-18 20:06:28', '2012-07-18 20:06:28', '', 1883, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1883-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(324, 2, '2011-11-18 01:00:42', '2011-11-18 01:00:42', '<strong><img class="alignright" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Flag_of_Thailand.svg/125px-Flag_of_Thailand.svg.png" alt="" width="125" height="83" />Thailand</strong> (<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loudspeaker.svg/11px-Loudspeaker.svg.png" alt="play" width="11" height="11" /> /ˈtaɪlænd/ <em><strong>ty</strong>-land</em> or /ˈtaɪlənd/<sup id="cite_ref-6">[7]</sup>; Thai: ประเทศไทย, RTGS: Prathet Thai), officially the <strong>Kingdom of Thailand</strong> (Thai: ราชอาณาจักรไทย,RTGS: Ratcha Anachak Thai; <small>IPA: </small>[râːt.tɕʰā ʔāːnāːtɕàk tʰāj]<small> (<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Speaker_Icon.svg/13px-Speaker_Icon.svg.png" alt="" width="13" height="13" /> listen)</small>), formerly known as <strong>Siam</strong> (Thai: สยาม; RTGS: Sayam), is a country located at the centre of the Indochina peninsula and Southeast Asia.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt is bordered to the north by Burma and Laos, to the east by Laos and Cambodia, to the south by the Gulf of Thailand and Malaysia, and to the west by theAndaman Sea and the southern extremity of Burma. Its maritime boundaries include Vietnam in the Gulf of Thailand to the southeast andIndonesia and India in the Andaman Sea to the southwest.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe country is a kingdom, with most recorded reigns in the world. It is aconstitutional monarchy with King Rama IX, the ninth king of the House of Chakri, who has reigned since 1946, making him the world''s longest-serving current head of state and the longest-reigning monarch in Thai history.<sup id="cite_ref-longestthai_7-0">[8]</sup> The king is officially titled Head of State, the Head of the Armed Forces, an Upholder of the Buddhist religion, and the Defender of all Faiths.', 'Thailand', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'thailand', '', '', '2012-01-30 11:10:14', '2012-01-30 11:10:14', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/?post_type=country&#038;p=324', 77, 'country', '', 0),
(203, 2, '2011-10-11 11:15:23', '2011-10-11 11:15:23', 'Cholera is spread by contaminated food and water. It is rare in travellers, as outbreaks tend to occur in areas with poor sanitation. An oral vaccine is available for those at risk (e.g. those working in slum areas, refugee camps or hospitals, those visiting friends and family in areas reporting cases, military personnel in conflict zones, and those visiting rural areas with recent outbreaks).', 'Cholera', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cholera', '', '', '2011-11-24 21:57:54', '2011-11-24 21:57:54', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/?post_type=vaccination&#038;p=203', 0, 'vaccination', '', 0),
