(210, 2, '2011-10-11 11:20:13', '2011-10-11 11:20:13', 'Diphtheria is uasually spread by close contact with infected persons. In the UK, the combined Diptheria/Tetanus/Polio vaccine is recommended when diphtheria boosters are indicated for adults. A diphtheria booster lasts 10 years. Tetanus is a serious infection, usually contracted following contamination of wounds. In the UK, after 5 doses of vaccine, tetanus boosters are not routinely required unless travelling to areas with limited medical care. In the UK, the combined Diptheria/Tetanus/Polio vaccine is recommended when tetanus boosters are indicated. A tetanus booster lasts 10 years.', 'Combined Diptheria/Tetanus & Polio (Revaxis)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'combined-tetanus-diptheria-polio-revaxis', '', '', '2011-10-13 14:12:53', '2011-10-13 14:12:53', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/?post_type=vaccination&#038;p=210', 0, 'vaccination', '', 0),
(211, 2, '2011-10-11 11:22:09', '2011-10-11 11:22:09', '<strong>About Hepatitis A</strong>\r\n\r\nHepatitis A is a viral infection which can cause severe liver disease. The viral infection is usually spread by contaminated food and water.\r\n\r\n<strong>Vaccination recommendation</strong>\r\n\r\nEffective hepatitis A vaccines are available, and boosters last up to 25 years.\r\n\r\nFind out what vaccines you need by selecting your destination <span style="text-decoration: underline;">here</span>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Hepatitis A', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hepatitis-a', '', '', '2011-11-21 14:02:42', '2011-11-21 14:02:42', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/?post_type=vaccination&#038;p=211', 0, 'vaccination', '', 0),
(212, 2, '2011-10-11 11:22:41', '2011-10-11 11:22:41', 'Hepatitis B is a viral infection which can cause serious liver disease. It is usually spread sexually and by contact with infected blood or body fluids (e.g. puncture of the skin with contaminated needles). Vaccination is recommended for long-stay travellers, and those at risk due to their medical history, activities or work.', 'Hepatitis B', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hepatitis-b', '', '', '2011-10-13 12:21:34', '2011-10-13 12:21:34', '', 0, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.com/?post_type=vaccination&#038;p=212', 0, 'vaccination', '', 0),
