(1643, 2, '2012-07-11 12:01:07', '2012-07-11 12:01:07', '<strong><img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/dr-bill-holmes.jpg" alt="Dr Bill Holmes" width="120" height="146" align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10" />“</strong>We pride ourselves in delivering our vaccination programmes to the highest clinical standards. Our primary focus is the safety and comfort of those receiving the vaccine.\r\n\r\nThe flu vaccines that we use are the same as those provided by the NHS, manufactured under guidance from the World Health Organisation, and in 2012 will also protect against swine flu.\r\n\r\nOur customers receive the best possible service and highest levels of medical care. Our vaccinations are delivered by qualified nurses who have received training in flu vaccine delivery. Nurses conduct the onsite clinics with comprehensive medical kits.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions regarding our clinical processes and practices, please contact operations director, Lyn Cousins at lyncousins@evguk.co.uk.<strong>”</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/dr-bill-holmes-signature.jpg" alt="Dr Bill Holmes'' signature" width="100" height="33" />\r\n\r\nDr Bill Holmes F.R.C.P, F.R.C.G.P, D.Occ.Med\r\nMedical Director\r\n\r\nTo book call <strong>0845 521 0030 </strong>and let Flu Fighters help defend your organisation.', 'Clinical Excellence', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '325-revision-14', '', '', '2012-07-11 12:01:07', '2012-07-11 12:01:07', '', 325, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/325-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1065, 2, '2012-01-12 10:13:23', '2012-01-12 10:13:23', 'A wide range of diseases in the tropics transmitted by mosquitoes. Malaria is transmitted by a mosquito that is most active at night, whereas denque fever, yellow fever and Japanese encephalitis transmitted by mosquitoes are most active during the day.\r\n\r\nTravel advice - insect bites\r\n\r\n* Wear long pants, socks and sweaters with long sleeves.\r\n* Wear like clothes in bright colors. Dark colors attract mosquitoes.\r\n* Use an insect repellent agent on the skin. Sleeping under a mosquito net impregnated against mosquitoes, every night. Sleeping anywhere in rooms with mosquito nets mounted on the windows or in rooms with air conditioning.\r\n* If your bedroom does not have air conditioning or mosquito nets for windows, the room should be sprayed with an insecticide.\r\n* The connectors can insect pin or local anesthetic creams used against itching and pain.\r\n\r\n\r\nTravel advice - mosquito nets\r\n\r\n* Along with the regular use of preventive anti-malarial drugs are mosquito nets around the bed the most effective method for preventing malaria.\r\n* The effect of bed nets increased 2-4 times by impregnation with permetrin or deltametrin.\r\n* Mosquito nets impregnated with permetrin is illegal to import, sell or use in the EU. Environmental Protection Agency is just now processing an application for permission to sell bed nets impregnated with deltametrin.\r\n* Consistent use of mosquito nets around the bed reduces the risk of getting malaria by approx. 50%. An impregnated nets should be re-impregnated at 6 months.\r\n* The mosquito net must be so large that it can be bent in under the mattress or sleeping pad and must hang loose so that you can not inadvertently come into contact with it during the night.\r\n\r\n\r\nTravel advice - insect repellents\r\n\r\n* In Denmark sold products AUTANES and Mosi-guard. These products are considered equivalent to such. Jungle Oil containing DEET and not available in Denmark.\r\n* AUTANES, Mosi-guard and DEET can irritate the skin and can not come in contact with mucous membranes, for example. eyes, nose and mouth. AUTANES should not be used on children under 3 years.\r\n* American Health Care recommends the use of DEET-containing products to children as young as 2 months. So Jungle Oil bought abroad can be used for the little ones.', 'Insect bites', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'insect-bites', '', '', '2012-06-18 10:20:38', '2012-06-18 10:20:38', '', 413, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.net/?page_id=1065', 0, 'page', '', 0),
