(1231, 2, '2012-01-25 12:25:57', '2012-01-25 12:25:57', '<h2>Our Scandinavian Heritage</h2>\r\nWe are the UK arm of the<strong> Danish Doctors Vaccination Service, DLVS,</strong>  founded in 1998 in Copenhagen. DLVS has grown steadily to become Denmark’s biggest vaccination service working with over 250 doctors and nurses in Denmark and has delivered more than 2.1 million vaccines. We offer an advice and vaccination service for travellers and flu jabs during high season from october-january.\r\n\r\nIn 2007, following the success of DLVS, the UK Travel Vaccination Service extended its services to the UK.\r\n\r\nThrough our <a title="The Flu Fighters website..." accesskey="f" tabindex="2" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/" target="_blank">Flu Fighters</a> campaign we are offering private and public sector organisations an on site vaccination service so that they can help to keep their staff free from seasonal flu.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1025-revision-5', '', '', '2012-01-25 12:25:57', '2012-01-25 12:25:57', '', 1025, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.net/1025-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1232, 2, '2012-01-25 12:32:40', '2012-01-25 12:32:40', '<h2></h2>\r\nWe are the UK arm of DLVS, Danish Doctors Vaccination Service, which was  founded in 1998 in Copenhagen. DLVS has grown steadily to become Denmark’s largest vaccination service working with over 250 doctors and nurses. DLVS has delivered more than 2.1 million vaccines. We offer an advice and vaccination service for travellers and flu jabs during flu season.\r\n\r\nIn 2007, following the success of DLVS, the <strong>UK Travel Vaccination Service</strong> extended its services to the UK.\r\n\r\nThrough our <a title="The Flu Fighters website..." accesskey="f" tabindex="2" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/" target="_blank">Flu Fighters</a> campaign we are offering private and public sector organisations an on site vaccination service so that they can help to keep their staff free from seasonal flu.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About UK Travel Vaccination Service', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1025-revision-6', '', '', '2012-01-25 12:32:40', '2012-01-25 12:32:40', '', 1025, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.net/1025-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1233, 2, '2012-01-25 12:42:37', '2012-01-25 12:42:37', '<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\nUK Travel Vaccination Service is the UK arm of DLVS, Danish Doctors Vaccination Service, which was  founded in 1998 in Copenhagen. DLVS has delivered more than 2.1 million vaccines. In 2007, following the success of DLVS, the UK Travel Vaccination Service extended its services to the UK.\r\n\r\nWe offer an advice and vaccination service for travellers and flu jabs during flu season.\r\n\r\nOur team has over 40 years experience in the UK healthcare sector and includes our Medical Director Dr William Holmes whose experience includes general practice, occupational health and respiratory medicine. All clinics are registred yellow fever centres and are care quality commisioned.\r\n\r\nThrough our <a title="The Flu Fighters website..." accesskey="f" tabindex="2" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/" target="_blank">Flu Fighters</a> campaign we are offering private and public sector organisations an on site vaccination service so that they can help to keep their staff free from seasonal flu.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1025-revision-7', '', '', '2012-01-25 12:42:37', '2012-01-25 12:42:37', '', 1025, 'http://dlvs-uk.konscript.net/1025-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
