(1470, 1, '2012-06-18 11:27:03', '2012-06-18 11:27:03', '[contact-form-7 id="197" title="dlvs-quote"]\r\n\r\nWe are here to keep your team fighting fit this winter.\r\nIf you have any questions about our service or would like to find out more, please contact us:\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Phone</span>: 0845 521 0030\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Email</span>: info@flufighters.org.uk\r\n\r\n<strong>European Vaccination Group (UK) Limited</strong>\r\n21a Brand Street,\r\nHitchin, Hertfordshire,\r\nSG5 1JE', 'Get A Quote', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1415-revision-8', '', '', '2012-06-18 11:27:03', '2012-06-18 11:27:03', '', 1415, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1415-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1296, 2, '2012-01-12 10:35:20', '2012-01-12 10:35:20', 'To travel is supposed to be equal to a number of good experiences. The good times may be overshadowed by illness and accidents. Fortunately, the vast majority of illnesses and accidents can be avoided if you just take some precautions.\r\n\r\nThis page tells you about these precautions.\r\n\r\nUnder each topic, there are facts about the disease and some practical advice you should follow before and during your trip.\r\n\r\nWe hope you have a great trip!', 'Travel Advice', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '413-revision-7', '', '', '2012-01-12 10:35:20', '2012-01-12 10:35:20', '', 413, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/413-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1538, 2, '2012-07-02 09:46:48', '2012-07-02 09:46:48', 'Flu Fighters make vaccinating your staff against seasonal flu a simple procedure.\r\n\r\nJust tell us the time, place and number of influenza vaccinations required and we do the rest.\r\n\r\nOur experienced team of nurses deliver a fully mobile flu vaccination service wherever you are in the UK with minimum disruption.\r\n\r\nOur nurses have all the equipment needed and we will ensure all the influenza vaccinations are delivered to the highest possible clinical standards.\r\n\r\nOnce you have decided to offer your employees the perk of a flu jab, we help you achieve maximum take-up levels. We help to ensure that your staff understand the health benefits that flu jabs can offer both at work and at home.\r\n\r\nThe best time to vaccinate your staff is between October and December. <a title="The Flu Fighters contact page..." accesskey="c" tabindex="24" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/contact-us">Contact us</a>, now to book your flu vaccines or request a <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/get-vaccination-quote">free flu vaccination quote online.</a>\r\n<h2>What to expect on the Day</h2>\r\nOn your chosen day the trained nurse(s) will arrive 15 minutes before the flu vaccination service is due to begin, with all the medical equipment required, and will ensure the vaccinations are delivered to the highest <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/clinical-excellence">clinical standards</a>.\r\n\r\nDisruption to you and your staff is minimal. It only takes a couple of minutes for the nurse to give the flu vaccination - through a small injection in the upper arm.\r\n\r\nAll we require from you is:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>A private room</li>\r\n	<li>Two chairs</li>\r\n	<li>A table</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a telephone</li>\r\n	<li>Drinking water</li>\r\n	<li>A washbasin</li>\r\n	<li>If there are windows in the room, blinds or curtains to provide staff privacy</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/fact_3.gif" alt="Flu Fact - A sneeze can reach over 100 miles an hour - so it''s no wonder flu can spread so fast, especially in crowded places" width="300" height="150" />', 'Our Service', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '413-revision-12', '', '', '2012-07-02 09:46:48', '2012-07-02 09:46:48', '', 413, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/413-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1297, 2, '2012-04-30 07:28:44', '2012-04-30 07:28:44', 'Flu Fighters make vaccinating your staff against seasonal flu a simple procedure.\r\n\r\nJust tell us the time, place and number of influenza vaccinations required and we do the rest.\r\n\r\nOur experienced team of nurses deliver a fully mobile flu vaccination service wherever you are in the UK with minimum disruption.\r\n\r\nOur nurses have all the equipment needed and we will ensure all the influenza vaccinations are delivered to the highest possible clinical standards.\r\n\r\nPlus, our service includes a 24 hour medical helpline for your employees who have received flu vaccine.\r\n\r\nOnce you have decided to offer your employees the perk of a flu jab, we help you achieve maximum take-up levels. We help to ensure that your staff understand the health benefits that flu jabs can offer both at work and at home.\r\n\r\nThe best time to vaccinate your staff is between October and December. <a title="The Flu Fighters contact page..." accesskey="c" tabindex="24" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/contact-us">Contact us</a>, now to book your flu vaccines or request a <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/get-vaccination-quote">free flu vaccination quote online.</a>\r\n<h1>What to expect on the Day</h1>\r\nOn your chosen day the trained nurse(s) will arrive 30 minutes before the flu vaccination service is due to begin, with all the medical equipment required, and will ensure the vaccinations are delivered to the highest <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/clinical-excellence">clinical standards</a>.\r\n\r\nDisruption to you and your staff is minimal. It only takes a couple of minutes for the nurse to give the flu vaccination - through a small injection in the upper arm.\r\n\r\nAll we require from you is:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>A private room</li>\r\n	<li>Two chairs</li>\r\n	<li>A table</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a telephone</li>\r\n	<li>Drinking water</li>\r\n	<li>A washbasin</li>\r\n	<li>If there are windows in the room, blinds or curtains to provide staff privacy</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/fact_3.gif" alt="Flu Fact - A sneeze can reach over 100 miles an hour - so it''s no wonder flu can spread so fast, especially in crowded places" width="300" height="150" />', 'Our Corporate Flu Vaccination Service', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '413-revision-8', '', '', '2012-04-30 07:28:44', '2012-04-30 07:28:44', '', 413, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/413-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1536, 2, '2012-04-30 07:43:04', '2012-04-30 07:43:04', '<strong></strong>We are the UK arm of the European Vaccination Group, which has delivered more than 2.5 million vaccines over the last 10 years, including to the blue-chip companies Shell, Motorola and Siemens.\r\n\r\nFlu Fighters is our campaign to promote the benefits of vaccination in the workplace, engage staff and maximise take up. Flu Fighters has also been designed to reflect the commitment of our team to offering the best vaccination service with the highest levels of dedication and clinical excellence.\r\n\r\nOur team has over 40 years experience in the UK healthcare sector and includes our Medical Director Dr William Holmes whose experience includes general practice, occupational health and respiratory medicine.\r\n\r\nTo find about more about the European Vaccination Group UK Limited visit: <a accesskey="v" tabindex="24" href="http://www.evguk.co.uk/" target="_blank">www.evguk.co.uk</a>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/fact_1.gif" alt="Flu Facts - A flu epidemic is when high levels of the disease occur suddenly in an area. Flu epidemics tend to happen every few years in the UK and cannot be predicted." width="300" height="150" hspace="10" vspace="10" />', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1025-revision-11', '', '', '2012-04-30 07:43:04', '2012-04-30 07:43:04', '', 1025, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1025-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1300, 2, '2012-01-26 08:22:47', '2012-01-26 08:22:47', '<strong></strong>UK Travel Vaccination Service is the UK arm of DLVS, Danish Doctors Vaccination Service, which was  founded in 1998 in Copenhagen. DLVS has delivered more than 2.1 million vaccines. In 2007, following the success of DLVS, the UK Travel Vaccination Service extended its services to the UK.\r\n\r\nWe offer an advice and vaccination service for travellers and flu jabs during flu season.\r\n\r\nOur team has over 40 years experience in the UK healthcare sector and includes our Medical Director Dr William Holmes whose experience includes general practice, occupational health and respiratory medicine. All clinics are registred yellow fever centres and are care quality commisioned.\r\n\r\nThrough our <a title="The Flu Fighters website..." accesskey="f" tabindex="2" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/" target="_blank">Flu Fighters</a> campaign we are offering private and public sector organisations an on site vaccination service so that they can help to keep their staff free from seasonal flu.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1025-revision-10', '', '', '2012-01-26 08:22:47', '2012-01-26 08:22:47', '', 1025, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1025-revision-10/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
