(1501, 1, '2012-06-20 16:27:06', '2012-06-20 16:27:06', 'UK Travel Vaccination Service - A trading name of The Health Station, is the UK arm of DLVS, Danish Doctors Vaccination Service, which was founded in 1998 in Copenhagen. DLVS has delivered more than 2.1 million vaccines. In 2007, following the success of DLVS, the UK Travel Vaccination Service extended its services to the UK.\r\n\r\nWe offer an advice and vaccination service for travelers and flu jabs during the flu season.\r\n\r\n<strong>Click the map to find the travel vaccinations you need</strong>:\r\n\r\n<a href="http://travelvaccination.co.uk/"><img src="http://flufighters.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/map-thumbnail2.jpg" alt="" title="Find travel vaccinations" width="632" height="375" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1499" /></a>\r\n\r\nOur team has over 40 years of experience in the UK healthcare sector and includes our Medical Director Dr William Holmes whose experience includes general practice, occupational health and respiratory medicine. All clinics are registered yellow fever centers and are care quality commissioned.', 'Travel Vaccination', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1498-revision-2', '', '', '2012-06-20 16:27:06', '2012-06-20 16:27:06', '', 1498, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1498-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
