(1636, 2, '2012-07-11 11:36:15', '2012-07-11 11:36:15', 'Flu Fighters make vaccinating your staff against seasonal flu a simple procedure.\r\n\r\nJust tell us the time, place and number of influenza vaccinations required and we do the rest.\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Our experienced team of nurses deliver a fully mobile flu vaccination service wherever you are in the UK with minimum disruption.</span>\r\n\r\nOur nurses have all the equipment needed and we will ensure all the influenza vaccinations are delivered to the highest possible clinical standards.\r\n\r\nOnce you have decided to offer your employees the perk of a flu jab, we help you achieve maximum take-up levels. We help to ensure that your staff understand the health benefits that flu jabs can offer both at work and at home.\r\n\r\nThe best time to vaccinate your staff is between October and December. <a title="The Flu Fighters contact page..." accesskey="c" tabindex="24" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/contact-us">Contact us</a>, now to book your flu vaccines or request a <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/get-vaccination-quote">free flu vaccination quote online.</a>\r\n<h2>What to expect on the Day</h2>\r\nOn your chosen day the trained nurse(s) will arrive 15 minutes before the flu vaccination service is due to begin, with all the medical equipment required, and will ensure the vaccinations are delivered to the highest <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/clinical-excellence">clinical standards</a>.\r\n\r\nDisruption to you and your staff is minimal. It only takes a couple of minutes for the nurse to give the flu vaccination - through a small injection in the upper arm.\r\n\r\nAll we require from you is:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>A private room</li>\r\n	<li>Two chairs</li>\r\n	<li>A table</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a telephone</li>\r\n	<li>Drinking water</li>\r\n	<li>A washbasin</li>\r\n	<li>If there are windows in the room, blinds or curtains to provide staff privacy</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Our Service', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '413-revision-16', '', '', '2012-07-11 11:36:15', '2012-07-11 11:36:15', '', 413, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/413-revision-16/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1539, 2, '2012-07-02 09:47:14', '2012-07-02 09:47:14', 'Flu Fighters make vaccinating your staff against seasonal flu a simple procedure.\r\n\r\nJust tell us the time, place and number of influenza vaccinations required and we do the rest.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Our experienced team of nurses deliver a fully mobile flu vaccination service wherever you are in the UK with minimum disruption.</em></span></strong>\r\n\r\nOur nurses have all the equipment needed and we will ensure all the influenza vaccinations are delivered to the highest possible clinical standards.\r\n\r\nOnce you have decided to offer your employees the perk of a flu jab, we help you achieve maximum take-up levels. We help to ensure that your staff understand the health benefits that flu jabs can offer both at work and at home.\r\n\r\nThe best time to vaccinate your staff is between October and December. <a title="The Flu Fighters contact page..." accesskey="c" tabindex="24" href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/contact-us">Contact us</a>, now to book your flu vaccines or request a <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/get-vaccination-quote">free flu vaccination quote online.</a>\r\n<h2>What to expect on the Day</h2>\r\nOn your chosen day the trained nurse(s) will arrive 15 minutes before the flu vaccination service is due to begin, with all the medical equipment required, and will ensure the vaccinations are delivered to the highest <a href="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/clinical-excellence">clinical standards</a>.\r\n\r\nDisruption to you and your staff is minimal. It only takes a couple of minutes for the nurse to give the flu vaccination - through a small injection in the upper arm.\r\n\r\nAll we require from you is:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>A private room</li>\r\n	<li>Two chairs</li>\r\n	<li>A table</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a telephone</li>\r\n	<li>Drinking water</li>\r\n	<li>A washbasin</li>\r\n	<li>If there are windows in the room, blinds or curtains to provide staff privacy</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<img src="http://www.flufighters.org.uk/sites/default/files/fact_3.gif" alt="Flu Fact - A sneeze can reach over 100 miles an hour - so it''s no wonder flu can spread so fast, especially in crowded places" width="300" height="150" />', 'Our Service', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '413-revision-13', '', '', '2012-07-02 09:47:14', '2012-07-02 09:47:14', '', 413, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/413-revision-13/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1540, 2, '2013-07-03 14:34:11', '2013-07-03 14:34:11', 'To all our corporate flu customers, we also offer an advice and vaccination service for travellers.\n\nOur services includes:\n<ul>\n	<li>Corporate travel vaccination for worldwide travelers at 13 conveniently located clinics in London, Birmingham, Leeds, Cambridge, Hitchin and St. Albans.</li>\n	<li>Opening hours 6 days a week</li>\n	<li>Anti malarial medicine</li>\n	<li>Vaccination certificates</li>\n	<li>Travel health advice</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Go to <a title="Travel Health advice" href="www.travelvaccination.co.uk" target="_blank">travelvaccination.co.uk</a> to find the travel vaccinations you need.   </strong>\n\n<a href="http://travelvaccination.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-1499" title="Find travel vaccinations" src="http://flufighters.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/map-thumbnail2.jpg" alt="" width="632" height="375" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;', 'Travel Vaccination', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1498-autosave', '', '', '2013-07-03 14:34:11', '2013-07-03 14:34:11', '', 1498, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1498-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1541, 2, '2012-06-20 16:31:55', '2012-06-20 16:31:55', 'UK Travel Vaccination Service - A trading name of The Health Station, is the UK arm of DLVS, Danish Doctors Vaccination Service, which was founded in 1998 in Copenhagen. DLVS has delivered more than 2.1 million vaccines. In 2007, following the success of DLVS, the UK Travel Vaccination Service extended its services to the UK.\r\n\r\nWe offer an advice and vaccination service for travelers and flu jabs during the flu season.\r\n\r\n<strong>Go to <a href="http://travelvaccination.co.uk/" target="_blank">http://travelvaccination.co.uk/</a> to find the travel vaccinations you need</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://travelvaccination.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-1499" title="Find travel vaccinations" src="http://flufighters.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/map-thumbnail2.jpg" alt="" width="632" height="375" /></a>\r\n\r\nOur team has over 40 years of experience in the UK healthcare sector and includes our Medical Director Dr William Holmes whose experience includes general practice, occupational health and respiratory medicine. All clinics are registered yellow fever centers and are care quality commissioned.\r\n\r\nOur services includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Travel vaccination for worldwide travelers at 2 conveniently located clinics in London</li>\r\n	<li>Opening hours 2 days a week</li>\r\n	<li>Anti malaria medicin</li>\r\n	<li>Vaccination certificates</li>\r\n	<li>Travel health advice</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Travel Vaccination', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1498-revision-9', '', '', '2012-06-20 16:31:55', '2012-06-20 16:31:55', '', 1498, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1498-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
