(1614, 2, '2012-07-11 08:47:19', '2012-07-11 08:47:19', 'We pride ourselves in delivering our vaccination programmes to the highest clinical standards. Our primary focus is the safety and comfort of those receiving the vaccine.\r\n\r\nOur vaccination service includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We deal exclusively in the provision of flu vaccinations to staff of UK employers</li>\r\n	<li>Our flu vaccine also protects against swine flu</li>\r\n	<li>Our service is quick, friendly, and easy to organise</li>\r\n	<li>We do not use agency nurses - our experienced, fully qualified will attend your requested location at a time that best suits both your business and staff needs, to administer flu vaccinations according to our stringent protocols governing clinical quality and excellence</li>\r\n	<li>We provide free delivery of all the materials required in advance and free removal/disposal of both clinical and paper waste after each session</li>\r\n	<li>We understand that protection of your workforce against flu needs to be both efficient and cost-effective – we therefore liaise closely year-on-year with the flu vaccine manufacturers to bring you the best possible deals available</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Put simply, flu vaccinations are our business – get in touch and let us start protecting yours!</strong></span>', 'Onsite flu jab for your staff', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1597-revision-3', '', '', '2012-07-11 08:47:19', '2012-07-11 08:47:19', '', 1597, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/1597-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
