(1633, 2, '2012-06-28 10:33:16', '2012-06-28 10:33:16', 'The WHO has announced the composition of the 2012/2013 flu vaccine. Each season, the vaccine compositon is reviewed and updated where needed to include the three strains most likely to cause illness. The new vaccine protects against two new strains, but still also includes protection against H1N1. Follow <a href="http://www.who.int/influenza/vaccines/virus/recommendations/201202_recommendation.pdf">this link</a> for the full technical details.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The WHO has announced the composition of the 2012/13 flu vaccine', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '44-revision-11', '', '', '2012-06-28 10:33:16', '2012-06-28 10:33:16', '', 44, 'http://flufighters.org.uk/44-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
